	},
	{
		"quote": "The first thing I did after joining The Rebellion was to re-title my “Tasks” list “Quests.”",
		"title": "Level Up Your Life: How to Unlock Adventure and Happiness by Becoming the Hero of Your Own Story",
		"author": "Steve Kamb"
	},
	{
