	},
	{
		"quote": "Worth noting here that a couple of years later, when I put a balance beam and some Weights on a table at the back of class, and just left it there without saying anything about it or trying to \"teach\" it, most of the children in the class, including some very poor students, figured out just by messing around with it how it worked.",
