		"quote": "Kanin’s 1994 article on false allegations is a provocative opinion piece, but it is not a scientific study of the issue of false reporting of rape. It certainly should never be used to assert a scientific foundation for the frequency of false allegations….It simply reflects the conclusions of…[police] officers whose procedures have been rejected by the U.S. Department of Justice and by the International Association of Chiefs of Police.",
