		"author": "Jon Krakauer"
	},
	{
		"quote": "The reaction to Will’s remarks was caustic and swift. “The last word I ever expected to hear to describe a rape victim is ‘privileged,’ ” wrote Jessica Valenti in the Guardian. “It takes a particular kind of ignorance to argue that people who come forward to report being raped in college are afforded benefits of any kind.”",
